text.section:
This section does not apply to:
the purchase, sale, or transportation of a handgun to or by a federally licensed gun dealer or manufacturer that provides or services a handgun for:
personnel of any unit of the federal government;
members of the armed forces of the United States or the National Guard;
law enforcement personnel of the State or any local law enforcement agency in the State while acting within the scope of their official duties; and
an organization that is required by federal law governing its specific business or activity to maintain handguns and applicable ammunition;
a firearm modified to be permanently inoperative;
the sale or transfer of a handgun by a federally licensed gun dealer or manufacturer covered under item (1) of this subsection;
the sale or transfer of a handgun by a federally licensed gun dealer or manufacturer to a lawful customer outside the State; or
an antique firearm.
